Revision history for App-podweaver

1.00    Version released at 2011-10-09-21:44.
        Updated copyright year.
        Added SEE ALSO section to POD.
        Make Build.PL autogenerate README from POD.
        Add configure_requires to Build.PL.
        Use /usr/bin/env perl shebang to play nice with perlbrew.

