        Move from deprecated Module::Build::ModuleInfo to Module::Metadata.

0.99_03 Version released at 2010-10-19-17:27.  *** Development version. ***
        Added missing Test::Command to build_requires.
        Remove "no package found" hacks: new Pod::Weaver handles this fine.

0.99_02 Version released at 2010-10-18-10:42.  *** Development version. ***
        Added optional configuration file for command-line defaults.
        Added basic tests for the command-line script.

0.99_01 Version released at 2010-10-12-13:25.  *** Development version. ***
        Initial release.
